akas: Teen Mom OG USA (fifth season title)
akas from release info: Teen Mom OG USA (fifth season title)

1.title: Icing on a Cake of Lies
1.plot: Amber loses her cool with Ryan's wife. Maci wants Ryan to complete rehab or she'll keep Bentley away. Catelynn worries about Tyler's dad Butch since he's off parole. Farrah celebrates her birthday in New York, while Amber calls off their engagement.

2.title: This Is Gonna End Badly
2.plot: Amber leans on her family while she figures out what to do about Matt. Ryan completes rehab early and demands to see Bentley. Catelynn worries if she gets pregnant again she'll have postpartum depression. Farrah looks for a home in Los Angeles.

3.title: Too Shady
3.plot: Farrah goes to Las Vegas for a girls trip and her ex-boyfriend Simon shows up. Catelynn and Tyler hurry to get everything ready for the launch of their children's clothing line. Maci lets Bentley see Ryan on Father's Day, while Amber kicks Matt out.

4.title: System Overload
4.plot: Maci asks for Ryan to take a drug test. Caitlyn and Tyler launch Tierra Reign. Farrah leaves Sophia with Michael to travel abroad. Amber continues to struggle with Matt.

5.title: High Hopes
5.plot: Farrah plans a family trip to Italy. Bentley starts third grade and Maci is still determined to keep him away from Ryan until he passes a drug test. Amber is depressed after breaking up with Matt. Catelynn and Tyler finally get a date to visit Carly.

6.title: That's a Wrap 2017
6.plot: You're invited to the party of the year with the casts of Teen Mom OG and Teen Mom 2! Join them in a swanky LA loft for a night of games, gossip, and fun as they celebrate 2017 and look ahead to 2018.

7.title: What a Ride
7.plot: Amber is completely done with Matt and starts dating a new guy. Farrah visits Omaha and Sophia expresses her dislike for Deb's fiancé, David. Taylor surprises Maci and takes her skydiving. Catelynn and Tyler finally get to see Carly.

8.title: Runways, Rehab, and Retail
8.plot: Amber and Catelynn unite at MTV's Video Music Awards. Tyler struggles with Butch's drug use. Farrah and Sophia model at NY fashion week. Maci and Taylor get an office for their business. Ryan is clean but Mackenzie still worries he may relapse.

9.title: Oh Baby
9.plot: Catelynn removes her birth control and doesn't tell Tyler. Farrah goes on a family vacation to Italy. Ryan and Mackenzie have a joint bachelor and bachelorette party. Maci learns Taylor is not invited to the wedding. Amber finds out she is pregnant.

10.title: Let's Try Again
10.plot: Farrah helps Michael plan his proposal. Catelynn freaks out at a photo shoot and Tyler is overwhelmed with launching the fall line. Maci and Taylor celebrate their one-year anniversary. (S7, ep9)

11.title: Fertile Myrtle
11.plot: Amber shocks her whole family when she reveals she's pregnant. Bentley turns 9 and Maci allows him to spend time with Ryan. Deb tries to persuade Sophia to go to her wedding. Catelynn secretly removed her IUD and has a big surprise for Tyler.

12.title: Unconfuse Your Brain
12.plot: Amber and Andrew have a disagreement. Ryan is furious at Maci when she shows up late to trick-or-treat. Farrah is shocked when she finds out who Deb invited to her wedding. Catelynn surprises her family with her pregnancy.

13.title: Something Blue
13.plot: Amber has big news for Leah. Farrah gets vaginal rejuvenation and lashes out at her producer. Catelynn spends quality time with Nova while Tyler gets emotional dropping Butch off at rehab. Maci and Taylor attend Ryan and Mackenzie's wedding.

14.title: Being Gary
14.plot: To celebrate Leah's 9th birthday, Gary plans a trip to Florida with his family and hopes to fix his difficult relationship with his mom, Carol. Meanwhile, his parents recently started dating each other again and a proposal is in the works.

15.title: I'm Beautiful, I'm Smart, I'm Strong
15.plot: Amber spends quality time with Leah while Gary gets a paternity test to find out if Jody is his father. Maci meets with a doctor to find new ways to manage her Polycystic Ovary Syndrome. Executive Producer Morgan heads to Austin to see Farrah.

16.title: Choose Your Path
16.plot: Tyler has a hard time running his business and taking care of Nova by himself. Maci trains to participate on another show. Amber starts preparing the nursery while Gary gets the paternity test results. Executive Producer Morgan speaks with Farrah.

17.title: Keep Chugging Away
17.plot: Amber takes Leah on vacation to Florida. Taylor takes Bentley on a boys trip to Jacksonville to visit their new clothing warehouse. Mackenzie enrolls in college and talks about kids with Ryan. Tyler and Nova visit Catelynn at her treatment facility.

18.title: Friends in Need
18.plot: Amber is angry at Gary and Kristina for saying she is a bad mother. Tyler struggles to keep their clothing business up and running while dealing with his dad and wife being in rehab. Maci visits Catelynn at her treatment facility.

19.title: Time Will Tell
19.plot: Maci and Taylor meet with an adoption counselor. Tyler and his sister Amber have an emotional reunion with their dad Butch when they visit him in rehab. Amber gives her cousin Krystal advice about co-parenting while Mackenzie and Ryan have big news.

20.title: One Life to Live
20.plot: Maci finds out from Bentley that Ryan and Mackenzie are expecting a baby. Amber is hurt when Leah chooses to sleepover at a friends house instead of spending time with her. Catelynn returns home but quickly admits herself again.

21.title: Teen Mom OG FInale Special: Check-Up with Dr. Drew Part 1
21.plot: Dr. Drew sits down with Maci, Catelynn, Amber, Farrah and their families for an uncensored discussion about all the biggest moments from this season of Teen Mom OG.

22.title: Teen Mom OG FInale Special: Check-Up with Dr. Drew Part 2
22.plot: Dr. Drew continues his discussion with Maci, Catelynn, Amber, and for the last time Farrah, to break down the biggest season of Teen Mom OG yet.

23.title: Teen Mom OG: Unseen Moments
23.plot: Enjoy never-before-seen footage from this season of Teen Mom OG as the moms - and for the first time, the dads - watch along with you.

24.title: Ask the Moms
24.plot: The moms of TMOG get together to answer everything you've been dying to know!

25.title: Meet the New Moms
25.plot: Meet The New Moms. Learn how Bristol's pregnancy was a hot topic during her mother, Sarah Palin's, Vice Presidential campaign and how Cheyenne's participation on MTV's The Challenge led to pregnancy.

26.title: Welcome to the Family
26.plot: Bristol returns home after a weekend away and has a heated argument with her husband. Cheyenne and Cory close co-parenting relationship causes issues with Cheyenne's boyfriend Zach. Amber welcomes her son James.

27.title: Unconditional Love
27.plot: Cheyenne's father finds out that her boyfriend Zach lives with her. Maci has an awkward handoff with Ryan's mom, Jen, while Amber realizes that despite her joy as a new mom, she's still struggling with depression.

28.title: Suns Out, Buns Out
28.plot: Bristol tries to stay positive after Dakota moves all her stuff into the guest bedroom, and Cheyenne causes a scene at her family's BBQ and misdirects her anger towards Zach. (S7, ep21)

29.title: Making Amends
29.plot: Bristol lets Tripp go to Alaska with his dad, Levi. Catelynn and Tyler visit Butch in rehab for the amends stage of his program. Gary and Kristina take Leah to visit Amber in LA. Maci finds out that Ryan was arrested

30.title: Mama Bear
30.plot: Catelynn finds out that Tyler's sister Amber trashed their old house. Amber's brother travels to LA to meet baby James. Cheyenne and Cory anxiously await results from Ryder's doctor's appointment for her genetic disorder, VLCAD.

31.title: Back to Square One
31.plot: Catelynn and Tyler celebrate Carly's birthday, whom they placed for adoption nine years ago and receive disappointing news. Bentley starts the 4th grade while Jen and Larry are relieved when Ryan returns to rehab.

32.title: New G's Meet the Old G's
32.plot: All of the moms fly to New York for press week and it's the first time Amber, Maci and Catelynn meet Cheyenne and Bristol. Meanwhile, Tyler visits Butch in his new sober living home in Austin.

33.title: Roll with the Punches
33.plot: Amber travels to LA for a charity boxing event and Andrew motivates her to step in the ring. Maci takes all the kids to Texas to visit Taylor's family. Catelynn finally takes steps to work on her marriage with Tyler.

42.plot: The cast of Teen Mom 2 takes you behind the scenes of an explosive finale special. See what really happens when all the girls get together and what goes down after they leave the stage.

0.title: Launch Special
0.plot: Before Maci, Farrah, Amber and Catelynn return as teenage mothers, the audience is presented with a look at the most significant moments from 16 and Pregnant.

1.title: Looking for Love
1.plot: Leah and Jeremy marry in Myrtle Beach. Javi has a big surprise for Kailyn. Jenelle, Barb, and Kieffer celebrate Jace's 3rd birthday but Jenelle reveals she has some serious money problem. Chelsea celebrates her 21st birthday.

2.title: How Many Chances
2.plot: Teen mom Maci contemplates breaking up with her fiancé, Ryan, Farrah starts dating a new guy even though her family disapproves. Amber struggles to get her GED, and Catelynn feels distant from her daughter since the adoption.

3.title: Fallout
3.plot: Catelynn's family lashes out over her choice of adoption while Amber and her fiancé Gary come to blows. Farrah learns that dating isn't easy, and Maci struggles to balance motherhood and school.

4.title: Moving On
4.plot: Amber and Gary's arguing finally reaches a boiling point, while Catelynn struggles to find a home when her mother moves away. Newly single mom Maci has a change of heart, and boy-crazy Farrah opts for some protection.

5.title: A Little Help
5.plot: Catelynn chooses adoption during a weekend retreat with other birth moms, while Maci and Ryan reach out to a counselor. Amber thinks about accepting help from her ex, and Farrah wonders if she should stay home more with her baby.

6.title: Standing Up
6.plot: Teenage mother Maci struggles with resenting her boyfriend, while Catelynn worries her boyfriend's father might go to jail. Farrah shifts her focus to her daughter, and Amber faces her fears about putting her baby in daycare.

7.title: Baby Steps
7.plot: Amber wants to put an end to the fighting and move away from Gary. Farrah can't stand living under her parents' roof anymore. Maci struggles to keep up in school when her son starts walking. Catelynn and Tyler plan their future.

8.title: Happy Birthday
8.plot: Catelynn & Tyler work on letting go of Carly, & Tyler works up the nerve to propose marriage to Catelynn. Maci and Ryan celebrate Bentley's first birthday. Amber copes with the pressures while planning Leah's 1st birthday.

9.title: Finale Special: Check Up with Dr. Drew
9.plot: A look back at the first year of motherhood for Maci, Amber, Catelynn and Farrah.

10.title: Unseen Moments
10.plot: Dr. Drew hosts a look at the exclusive moments we never saw with Farrah, Maci, Catelynn and Amber from the first season of Teen Mom.

1.title: Not Again
1.plot: Farrah calls the police on her own mother. Amber faces a pregnancy scare. Maci takes her ex, Ryan, to court for child support. Catelynn is upset that she has to move out of her boyfriend's house and back in with her family.

2.title: Should I Stay or Should I Go?
2.plot: Catelynn gets caught in a lie. Amber's boyfriend might leave her for someone else. Farrah juggles college, a new job and moving houses - all with her daughter Sophia. Maci tries to move into a house with her college friends.

3.title: Valentine's Day
3.plot: Maci reconnects with an old flame on Valentine's Day. Their crying baby and unrealistic expectations ruin Amber and Gary's romantic dinner. Catelynn's boyfriend struggles about the adoption. Farrah reveals an emotional secret.

4.title: Spring Break
4.plot: Amber and Gary take a vacation. Maci and Ryan butt heads over Ryan's new girlfriend. Farrah's mom is offered a plea bargain for their physical altercation. Catelynn finds out Tyler is still angry at her about a past lie.

5.title: Secrets & Lies
5.plot: Catelynn and Tyler find their high school romance back on the rocks, a big fight makes Amber question her engagement to Gary, Maci introduces her new boyfriend to her son Bentley and Farrah gets scammed.

6.title: Trial and Error
6.plot: Maci questions whether her new boyfriend is ready to date a teen mom while Farrah tries speed dating. Amber works toward her GED and Catelynn's stepdad is court-ordered to rehab, leaving her alone with her guilt-inducing mom.

7.title: Senior Prom
7.plot: An argument about the adoption ruins Catelynn's prom dress shopping; Maci is upset when Ryan says he's taking her to court over custody of Bentley. Farrah goes to counseling with her mom and Gary ruins Amber's birthday plans.

8.title: Hello and Goodbye
8.plot: Chelsea is frustrated about having to move. Leah finally makes a decision about who she wants to be with. Jenelle gets in a fight with Kieffer. Kailyn and Javi take the big step in their relationship.

9.title: Family Bonds
9.plot: Farrah reaches out to Sophia's dad's family in an attempt to get Social Security benefits for Sophia. Maci tells Ryan she is moving to Nashville, while Catelynn and Tyler learn Butch has ended up back in jail.

10.title: Lashing Out
10.plot: Amber lashes out at Gary when he threatens to take Leah away. Catelynn and Tyler find out they will not graduate from High School on time. Maci tries to work out a visitation schedule with Ryan. Farrah has an emotional reunion.

11.title: Too Much, Too Soon
11.plot: Maci confronts Kyle about her new life in Nashville. Catelynn and Tyler learn they will get to go visit Carly for the first time in a year. Amber breaks it off with Gary. Farrah learns the results of Sophia's DNA test.

12.title: See You Later
12.plot: A year after the adoption, Catelynn and Tyler have an emotional reunion with their daughter. Amber & Gary try to work out custody of Leah. Farrah's mom sets her up on a date. Maci and Ryan battle over parental rights.

0.title: Catching up with the Girls
0.plot: Special episode recapping the emotional journeys of 16 and Pregnant's Chelsea, Jenelle, Catelynn and Leah; and a look forward at their upcoming season of Teen Mom which follows their challenges in the first year of motherhood.

1.title: Taking It Slow
1.plot: Teen Mom Maci confronts her ex about child support. Amber chooses between her baby's dad and her new boyfriend. Catelynn and Tyler consider moving in together while still in high school, and Farrah considers making a big change.

2.title: To Be with You
2.plot: Amber and Gary move in together while Tyler's family questions his decision to move in with Catelynn. Maci considers letting her boyfriend move in with her and Bentley to make ends meet - and Farrah struggles with being away from Sophia.

3.title: The Last Straw
3.plot: Amber finds out that she is being investigated, and fears she will lose custody. Ryan wants to meet Maci's new boyfriend, while Sophia's paternal grandmother is suing for visitation rights. Tyler's dad gets out of jail.

4.title: Trials and Tribulations
4.plot: Catelynn struggles to fix her relationship with her mom, while Amber & Gary meet with Child Protective Services. Maci finally decides to move away from Kyle and back home to Chattanooga, and Farrah goes to court.

5.title: Trick or Treat
5.plot: Maci and Ryan argue over who has rights to Bentley on his birthday, and Amber breaks down over being separated from Leah. Farrah struggles to spend time with Sophia, and Catelynn and Tyler look for jobs.

6.title: Terrible Twos
6.plot: Amber is upset when Gary refuses to celebrate Leah's birthday together, and Catelynn copes with her fears about adoption. Farrah gets a puppy, while Maci's Ex finally discovers that her boyfriend is living with her.

7.title: Without You
7.plot: Farrah takes her daughter Sophia on a trip to visit Sophia's dad's grave, and Amber and her mom get in an argument. Maci struggles to keep up in college, while Catelynn and Tyler want to invite their daughter to graduation.

8.title: Taking It Up a Notch
8.plot: Amber goes on a date, while Catelynn and Tyler get their parents involved with planning a perfect Christmas. Maci makes a shocking announcement, and Farrah breaks the news to her parents that she wants to move to California.

9.title: As Long as We're Together
9.plot: Farrah and her parents argue while on a trip, and Catelynn reunites with her father. Amber reaches out to Gary to re-unite her family on the anniversary of a tragedy, while Maci considers withdrawing from school.

10.title: Stay with Me
10.plot: Amber spends the night in jail, and finds out that a no-contact order has been put on her and Gary. Catelynn and Tyler have a falling out, and Farrah explores moving to Florida. Maci is overwhelmed while taking care of Bentley.

11.title: Time Out
11.plot: Maci has a blowout with Ryan over custody, while Amber and Gary struggle with a no-contact order. Catelynn finally finishes high school, and Farrah's parents try to talk her into leaving Sophia behind when she moves away.

12.title: Pros & Cons
12.plot: Amber and Gary try to get the no-contact order lifted, while Maci tries to cut Ryan out of her life. Farrah makes an unexpected choice about moving away, and Butch moves in with Catelynn and Tyler.

13.title: Unseen Moments
13.plot: Dr. Drew hosts an exclusive look at never-before seen laughs, struggles and other drama from Season 3 with Farrah, Maci, Catelynn, and Amber.

14.title: Check-Up with Dr. Drew: Part 1
14.plot: In part one of the finale special, Farrah and Amber reflect on the past year of motherhood - the struggles, triumphs, legal battles, and family strife that we saw them face in Season 3, and everything that has happened.

15.title: Check-Up with Dr. Drew: Part 2
15.plot: In part two Catelynn and Maci discuss the new milestones, custody battles, school struggles, and family problems that we saw them face in Season 3, and Ryan and Kyle share the stage for the first time.

1.title: Separation Anxiety
1.plot: Maci decides to enroll Bentley in daycare while Amber prepares to go to rehab. Catelynn and Tyler celebrate Carly's second birthday, and Farrah has a change of heart about leaving daughter Sophia behind when she moves.

2.title: Letting Go
2.plot: Catelynn and Tyler have an emotional visit with their daughter. Amber struggles during her first weeks of rehab. Farrah says farewell to her life in Iowa. A disagreement with Ryan disrupts Maci and Kyle's relationship.

3.title: The Places You'll Go
3.plot: Catelynn and Tyler attend their high school graduation. Maci considers joining Ryan on his family vacation. Farrah has to deal with her parents' overbearing concerns. In rehab, Amber expects a visit from Gary and Leah.

4.title: Strike Out
4.plot: Gary and Leah visit Amber in rehab, and Farrah goes on a date with her neighbor. Maci tags along on Ryan's family vacation and Catelynn and Tyler question letting Butch move back into their home.

5.title: Homecoming
5.plot: Amber and Gary work on their relationship issues. Maci struggles to choose classes. Visiting her parents, Farrah is annoyed with their concerns for Sophia. Catelynn and her grandmother attend a birth parent support group.

6.title: Temper Tantrums
6.plot: A visit from Farrah's mom and sister leads to a blowup, and Maci enrolls her son Bentley in preschool. Catelynn and Tyler face issues with Butch, while Amber debates leaving rehab early.

7.title: Fresh Start
7.plot: Maci and Ryan clash over Bentley attending preschool. Tyler pressures Catelynn to enroll in college. Farrah begins dating a new guy. After completing two months in rehab, Amber finally heads back home.

8.title: The Next Step
8.plot: Maci and Kyle contemplate buying a house. Farrah introduces Sophia to her new boyfriend. Amber struggles to find a way to see her daughter. A fight between Catelynn and Tyler's parents throw their family future into question.

9.title: By the Rules
9.plot: Farrah introduces her boyfriend to Debra. Catelynn supports her own mom as Tyler's dad goes to court. Bentley has a hard time adjusting to Maci's new house. Amber and Gary continue to struggle with sharing custordy of Leah.

10.title: Change of Plans
10.plot: In a visit to Texas, Farrah challenges Daniel about their relationship. Maci and Ryan argue about Ryan's new girlfriend. Amber looks for a new home for her and Leah. Catelynn and Tyler struggle to make a decision about college.

11.title: For the Best
11.plot: Bentley's birthday leads to a blowout between Maci and Ryan. Farrah spends time with Sophia before saying goodbye for a month. Amber and Gary come up with a custody plan for Leah. Catelynn and Tyler help their parents cope.

12.title: Wake Up
12.plot: Amber has second thoughts about giving Gary full custody. Catelynn helps Tyler cope with emotions about his dad and they both reflect on the adoption. Farrah misses Sophia. Ryan confronts Maci about their custody arrangement.

13.title: Finale Special: Part 1
13.plot: Dr. Drew talks with Catelynn and Farrah about the final season of Teen Mom, along with updates on the lives of the original Teen Moms.

14.title: Finale Special: Part 2
14.plot: Dr. Drew talks with Maci and Amber about the final season of Teen Mom, along with updates on the lives of the original Teen Moms.

15.title: Unseen Moments 4
15.plot: Dr. Drew presents never-before-seen clips from Maci, Amber, Catelynn, and Farrah and of the final season of Teen Mom.

16.title: Farewell Special
16.plot: Featuring never-before-seen footage from their casting tapes, behind-the-scenes secrets, and dramatic updates on where they are now, Maci, Catelynn, Farrah, and Amber say goodbye with a look back on their journeys from being 16 and pregnant to today.

17.title: Amber Behind Bars
17.plot: Dr. Drew visits Amber in prison to find out how the teen mom is adjusting to life behind bars.

18.title: Ask the Moms
18.plot: Teen Mom fans finally get a chance to ask Maci, Farrah, Amber, and Catelynn (and the major players in their lives) all the questions they've been dying to know.

0.title: Teen Mom OG Catch Up Special
0.plot: Catch up with original girls who started it all and relive Catelynn, Maci, and Amber's journeys as they navigate being 16 and pregnant to the Teen Mom's they are today.

1.title: Back and Better Than Ever
1.plot: Cate and Tyler find out they are pregnant so Cate wants to get married in a courthouse. Maci struggles co-parenting with Ryan. Amber falls for Gary's flirting, but then is crushed when he goes on a family vacation with his new girlfriend and Leah.

2.title: Back to School
2.plot: Catelynn and Tyler plan a party to go public with their baby's gender. Maci has a hard time believing Bentley is starting kindergarten. Gary asks Amber to help out with Leah's first day of kindergarten.

3.title: Old Wounds
3.plot: Tyler posts a video of Carly on their fan page which upsets Brandon and Teresa. Maci continues struggling to communicate with Ryan about co-parenting. Amber is extremely hurt by Gary because he won't let Leah spend the night.

4.title: New Kids on the Block
4.plot: Catelynn learns that Brandon and Teresa want to discuss adoption issues. Maci reveals that she and Taylor are expecting a baby. Amber discovers that Gary and Kristina are also expecting a baby of their own.

5.title: Surprise, Surprise
5.plot: Cate and Tyler meet with Brandon and Teresa. Maci tells Ryan and his family she's having a baby with Taylor. Amber confronts Gary about his flirting. Farrah is hurt after not bring a part of the season from the beginning.

6.title: The F Bomb
6.plot: Cate finds out she has gestational diabetes. Farrah struggles with her mom's visit. Amber reveals her relationship with her boyfriend and Maci quits the show when she finds out Farrah is back.

7.title: First Time for Everything
7.plot: Maci returns to the series, but has conditions regarding Bentley. Catelynn and Tyler struggle with being first time parents and they get a special gift from Teresa. Farrah introduces her boyfriend Simon to her mother. Matt proposes to Amber.

8.title: Mom vs. Mom
8.plot: Amber, Farrah, Maci and Cate come together in New York to do press for the show. The tension between Farrah and the rest of the girls comes to a head when Farrah discovers that Maci had quit the series because of her.

9.title: Boiling Point
9.plot: Tyler puts pressure on Cate to lose her pregnancy weight. Things boil over between Amber and Matt in Vegas. Maci worries about Bentley's safety while in Ryan's care and Debra attempts to go into business with Farrah.

10.title: Let's Face It
10.plot: Amber's family questions Matt's intentions when his past is revealed. Catelynn leaves Nova under April's care. Maci and Taylor find their dream home. Simon meets Sophia and Farrah pressures him for an engagement.

11.title: Why Can't We Just Get Along
11.plot: Farrah realizes her relationship with Simon is over. Amber asks Gary for joint custody while Maci invites Ryan to hang out. Tyler's dad Butch is released from prison and meets Nova for the first time.

12.title: Playing for Keeps
12.plot: Farrah asks her mother to watch Sophia for a month; Amber is blindsided by Leah's wishes; Maci does not want Bentley at Ryan's parents' house.

13.title: Party Down
13.plot: Farrah gets kicked out of a Party. Amber struggles with Gary's new visitation schedule for Leah. Catelynn and Tyler have their bachelor and bachelorette parties while Maci is frustrated that Taylor hasn't proposed.

14.title: Never Say Goodbye
14.plot: Farrah has a hard time taking Sophia to visit Derek's family; Ryan is annoyed about the amount of control Maci has over Bentley; Catelynn deals with anxiety.

15.title: The Big Day
15.plot: Catelynn and Tyler finally say 'I do'! Maci and Taylor buy an online t-shirt business while Amber and Matt decide to flip houses. Farrah and Debra argue when Farrah lets her know she doesn't trust her to take care of Sophia.

16.title: Skeletons in the Closet
16.plot: Farrah leaves for a month long business trip and has a last minute change of heart on who can watch Sophia while she is away. Maci and Ryan celebrate Bentley's 7th birthday together while Catelynn has post wedding.

17.title: Forgive & Forget
17.plot: Farah returns from her business trip and shares a life changing decision with her parents. Maci and Ryan celebrate Halloween as a family while Catelynn and Tyler go to Hawaii for their honeymoon.

18.title: Honeymoon Is Over
18.plot: Simon comes back into Farrah's life and Catelynn and Tyler are concerned when Butch starts dating.Maci is overwhelmed with life and needs Taylor to step it up and Amber wants to take Leah on a trip but Gary has all the power.

19.title: Taking Chances
19.plot: Farrah and Simon decide to take their relationship to the next level. Maci is annoyed she does all the work for Taylor's t-shirt business while Ryan plans a big move. Cate learns she has post-partum depression.

20.title: Walk Away
20.plot: Maci is shocked that Ryan is stepping up as a father while Cate and Tyler celebrate Nova's first birthday, but Butch and April have to be separated. Amber and Gary work out their custody battle over Leah, and Farrah gets into an argument with production.

21.title: Teen Mom OG: Check-Up with Dr. Drew - Part One
21.plot: Dr. Drew sits down with Maci & Farrah to dig deeper into their emotional journeys this season. From Maci's joy that her and Ryan can finally co-parent to Farrah's romance with Simon & fiery final moment.

22.title: Teen Mom OG: Check-Up with Dr. Drew - Part Two
22.plot: In part two, Catelynn breaks down over her depression and Tyler and Butch open up about their individual childhoods. Amber and Matt confront Gary over exposing Matt's numerous child support cases.

1.title: Put a Ring on It
1.plot: Amber and Gary finally settle their custody dispute over Leah. Farrah plans a move to LA, but questions her relationship with Simon. Catelynn and Tyler debate having another baby.

2.title: Tweet Tweet
2.plot: Farrah's mom confronts Simon at Sophia's 7th birthday party after he posts an old mugshot of her on social media. Amber deals with the latest rumor in the media about Matt.

3.title: Don't Panic
3.plot: Maci and Taylor find out she's further along in her unexpected pregnancy than they thought, Matt takes Amber to his hometown where she meets one of his family members.

4.title: Animal Instincts
4.plot: Maci and Taylor plan their wedding. Leah is hurt after Amber misses a visit with her. Farrah invites Simon to celebrate Easter with her family, and then kicks him out due to his lack of enthusiasm.

5.title: Hello, Goodbye
5.plot: Catelynn and Tyler say goodbye so she can attend a treatment facility; Maci and Taylor buy a larger house.

6.title: Second Guessing
6.plot: Maci and Taylor question their decision to have their wedding so soon; Farrah and Simon get relationship advice from Dr. Jenn; Tyler and Nova visit a homesick Catelynn at a treatment facility.

7.title: The Long Road Home
7.plot: Maci's daughter Jayde turns one; Farrah makes a big move to Los Angeles, but continues to fight with Simon when he tries to help.

8.title: Mother's Day
8.plot: Maci and Taylor welcome their third child but still worry that Ryan isn't showing up enough for Bentley. Gary tries to co-parent with Amber but realizes there's still tension between them. Farrah decides she's ready to move on from Simon, and Tyler attempts to be more sensitive towards Catelynn as she adjusts to life at home

9.title: The Tipping Point
9.plot: Amber worries she's developed a new addiction to food and consults a doctor about her weight. Farrah decides to open a frozen yogurt shop, while Tyler's concerned that Catelynn is falling back into her old, bad habits. Ryan and his dad Larry get into a huge fight that forces Ryan to finally leave their house, and causes Maci to worry that Bentley will be caught in the middle.

10.title: Lemons Into Lemonade
10.plot: Amber and Gary get ready for Leah's first day of school, while Catelynn continues to struggle with her anxiety and depression. Ryan takes Bentley for the weekend even though Maci isn't convinced he's changed, and the grand opening of Farrah's frozen yogurt store is made all the more interesting when Simon shows up to help.

11.title: Surprise Surprise!
11.plot: Amber and Matt attempt to put a stop to the tabloid rumors surrounding them, but are sidetracked by a visit from Matt's troubled son while Farrah deals with an employee at FroCo that's not living up to her high standards. Tyler and Catelynn celebrate Butch's first year out of prison, while Taylor and Bentley plan something special for Maci's birthday.

12.title: The Ties That Bind
12.plot: Jenelle walks down the aisle and Chelsea celebrates her marriage. Leah tries to get Addie ready for her first day of preschool. Kailyn has her baby and Javi comes face to face with what could have been. Briana's mother and Devoin nearly come to blows

13.title: Ginger's Last Binger
13.plot: Farrah and her mother uncover old family wounds and get into a huge fight. Matt is offered the opportunity to write a book about his life, but he and Amber are distracted by the latest tabloid stories that now involve Christopher. Maci and Taylor head to Las Vegas to celebrate at their bachelor and bachelorette parties. And Cate considers buying a horse to help with her anxiety.

14.title: Cray Gardens
14.plot: Gary reluctantly asks Amber for help with Leah when Kristina has a family emergency. Maci gets to know Ryan's new girlfriend better, while Catelynn and Tyler discover they're still not ready to move into their new home. Farrah receives some surprisingly helpful advice from Simon as she continues to fight with her mother.

15.title: I Do!
15.plot: Amber undergoes plastic surgery in an attempt to relieve her depression and negative self image issues, while Farrah and her mom try to reconcile their differences after an awkward encounter with Debra's boyfriend. Catelynn and Tyler get some bad news about Butch, and Maci and Taylor finally tie the knot

16.title: A Fresh Start
16.plot: Maci and Ryan try to coordinate trick or treating with Bentley. Amber is excited about her new business venture, but is let down when Gary doesn't let Leah stay with her on a school night.

17.title: Hello Again World!
17.plot: Tyler's less optimistic than usual when his dad is released from prison again. Farrah and Simon consider the status of their relationship. Maci throws Bentley a birthday party and is pleasantly surprised with Ryan. Amber extends an olive branch to Gary.

18.title: Lil' Starburst
18.plot: Catelynn and Tyler celebrate Nova's birthday and consider having another baby, while Farrah makes a big decision about her and Sophia's future. Amber works with Gary to throw Leah a birthday party.

19.title: Blue Christmas
19.plot: Amber continues to be frustrated that she doesn't have Leah as much as she wants, while Ryan's girlfriend encourages him to communicate more with Maci about Bentley's schedule. Cate surprises Tyler with a winter getaway.

29.title: Teen Mom OG Finale Special: Check-up with Dr. Drew - Part One
29.plot: In Part 1 of the "Teen Mom OG" Finale Special, Dr. Drew talks to Catelynn about her battle with depression and anxiety, and when Amber gets upset over her battles with Farrah and Gary, she threatens to quit the show.

30.title: Ask the Moms
30.plot: Catelynn, Maci, and Amber get real - and real emotional - when answering fan questions about the show and their lives off-screen.

31.title: Teen Mom OG Finale Special: Check-in with Dr. Drew - Part Two
31.plot: Farrah explains her dislike for her mom's fiance, and Catelynn opens up about how she and Tyler have dealt with Butch's relapse.
